        div(class="block md:hidden -mb-16")
          div(class="relative overflow-y-scroll mx-auto shadow-lg rounded-md" style="max-height: 600px; width: 90%;")
            img(src="/static/images/landing/product-image-hq.png" alt="Haptic - product page example" class="w-full" style="max-width: 1200px;")

  // - features
  div(class="relative overflow-x-hidden")
    img(src="/static/images/landing/shapes/lines-1.svg" alt="Lines background" class="fixed mt-32 left-1/2" style="min-width: 2300px; min-height: 2300px; transform: translateX(-50%)")
    main(class="relative mt-48 lg:mt-64 overflow-x-hidden")
      div(class="mb-32")
        div(class="container mx-auto p-4")
          div(class="relative mx-auto")
            img(src="/static/images/landing/shapes/blob-1.svg" alt="Blob shape" class="absolute -top-2 -left-24 opacity-50")

            div(class="relative z-10")
              span(class="text-xs text-gray-600 font-medium uppercase text-center block mb-1 mx-auto" style="max-width: 22ch;") Why I built Haptic?
              h3(class="font-bold text-center mx-auto text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-28 sm:mb-16") The idea is simple

              div(class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-8 gap-8 mt-32")
                div(class="col-span-8 md:col-span-4 lg:col-span-3")
                  div(class="relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-md bg-opacity-70 bg-clip-padding" style="backdrop-filter: blur(20px);")
                    img(src="/static/images/landing/me-bw-optimized.jpg" class="absolute -top-20 left-1/2 rounded-full w-32 h-32 shadow-2xl border-4 border-gray-500" style="transform: translateX(-50%);" alt="Borislav Grigorov")
                    div(class="mt-12 p-4 md:p-8")
                      p(class="mb-4 md:mb-8") Hey, there! 👋
                      p(class="mb-4 md:mb-8") I'm Borislav &mdash; full-stack developer, part time indie maker.
                      p Let me tell you about Haptic 👉
                      hr(class="mb-4 md:my-8 hidden")
                div(class="col-span-8 md:col-span-4 lg:col-span-5")
                  div(class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-md bg-opacity-70 bg-clip-padding p-4 pt-6 md:p-8 md:pt-8 mb-8 relative" style="backdrop-filter: blur(20px);")
                    span(class="text-xs uppercase text-gray-600 font-medium bg-yellow-100 px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 absolute -top-4 left-8 shadow border border-yellow-300") The problem
                    p(class="mb-4 md:mb-8") When I started to #BuildInPublic, I quickly realized that the general process is a mess.                
                    p(class="mb-4 md:mb-8") I was using countless platforms to share my ups, downs and learnings. The content creation tools were limited and sometimes constraining.
                    p(class="mb-4 md:mb-8") On top of that my posts were living in context of other personal sharings, unrelated to my #BuildInPublic journey.
                    p(class="lg:absolute lg:-bottom-18 lg:-right-4 lg:bg-white lg:rounded-md lg:border lg:border-gray-200 lg:max-w-lg lg:p-4 bg-clip-padding bg-opacity-70" style="backdrop-filter: blur(20px);") I was unable to create tractable, coherent story around the product itself. Everything was swallowed in feeds and lost in the void.

                  div(class="flex-1 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-md p-4 pt-6 md:p-8 md:pt-8 relative lg:mt-32 bg-clip-padding bg-opacity-70" style="backdrop-filter: blur(20px);")
                    span(class="text-xs uppercase text-gray-600 font-medium bg-yellow-100 px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 absolute -top-4 left-8 shadow border border-yellow-300") The solution
                    p(class="mb-4 md:mb-8") Haptic aims to streamline the process. It provides a set of content creation tools which help you narrate a coherent story.
                    p(class="mb-4 md:mb-8") Think of Haptic as your product's public diary.
                    p Having it all in one place makes it easier for your audience to engage and enjoy the ride with you.

      div(class="relative")
        div(class="container mx-auto p-4")
          span(class="text-xs text-gray-600 font-medium uppercase text-center block mb-1") The essence 
          h3(class="font-bold text-center mx-auto text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-28 sm:mb-16") How it works

          div(class="my-8 mb-16 flex items-center")
            a(href="/how-to-build-in-public" title="How to build in public" class="relative z-10 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50  rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-lg text-center inline-block mx-auto click-scale shadow-sm hover:shadow-md") Read our guide on how to build in public

          +step(1, "Create your product page", "create-product", 72, "blob-1", { class: "-top-4 -left-10 opacity-40" }, 300)
            div(class="relative z-10")
              p(class="mb-4") It takes 5 seconds.
              p(class="mb-4") You'll get a unique slug for your product page on #[strong haptic.so/p/{your-slug}].
              p This is your public url.
          +step(2, "Build rich narratives", "icons", 48, "blob-2", { class: "-top-24 -right-10 opacity-30" }, 400)
            p(class="mb-4") You have various tools at your disposal to share your jorney with the crowd.
            // - p Quick update posts, long-form articles, feedback surveys, milestone celebrations, roadmaps and more.
          +step(3, "Collect products, show some ❤️", "boost-collect", 44, "blob-3", { class: "top-10 left-10 opacity-60" }, 350)
            p(class="mb-4") Make a collection of products that you love, built by fellow makers on haptic.
            p Boost your most favorite ones to show its creators that you care.

      div(class="relative mb-32")
        div(class="container mx-auto p-4")
          span(class="text-xs text-gray-600 font-medium uppercase text-center block mb-1") There's more
          h3(class="font-bold text-center mx-auto text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-4") The details

          div(class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-600 font-medium text-center mb-28 sm:mb-16 mx-auto" style="max-width: 24ch;")
            p Haptic aims to streamline your #BuildInPublic experience.
            p Here's how:

          ul(class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 lg:gap-8")
            +detail("Build in the open")
              p Be the inspiration for the fellow makers.
            +detail("Make collections")
              p Found a story worth following? Add it to your collection.
            +detail("Boosts")
              p Show some love - boost your favorite products.
            +detail("Quick updates")
              p Just share your thoughts. No stress.
            +detail("Tools")
              p Brag about your stack!
            +detail("Markdown support")
              p Because WYSIWYG is not always what you get.
            +detail("Long-form content", true)
              p Dive into the details.
            +detail("(Haptic) Feedback", true)
              p You're not sure about your logo? You need to decide on the next feature? Just ask your crowd!
            +detail("Celebrations", true)
              p Share your milestones.
            +detail("Roadmaps", true)
              p Get specific on how your ideas will come to reality.
            +detail("Browse products", true)
              p Browse products built publicly on Haptic. Find amazing stories. Get inspired.
            +detail("Streaks", true)
              p Let the compounding effect do it's magic. You just have to show up.
            +detail("Rankings", true)
              p Let's play the game. 🚀

      div(class="mb-32")
        div(class="container mx-auto p-4")
          span(class="text-xs text-gray-600 font-medium uppercase text-center block mb-1") Popular usecases
          h3(class="font-bold text-center mx-auto text-3xl lg:text-4xl mb-28 sm:mb-16") Who is Haptic built for

          div(class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16")
            +use-case("Makers", "hexagon", "shape-1") For the problem-solvers, who create reusable solutions.
            +use-case("Writers", "edit-2", "shape-2") For those, who tame the words for us.
            +use-case("Learners", "book-open", "shape-3") For all of us, who master the chaos of knowledge.
            +use-case("Designers", "pen-tool", "shape-4") For the people, who deliver elegant usability.
            +use-case("Artists", "circle", "shape-5") For the creative ones, who can deeply touch our souls.
            +use-case("You", "heart", "shape-6") For You and your story. Whoever you are. Whatever your story.

          div(class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center")
            a(class="btn btn-primary text-lg md:text-xl px-6 py-4 inline-block click-scale mb-2" href=("/login")) Start sharing your story
            span(class="text-sm text-gray-600") FREE, no credit cards required!
            +people

      div(class="mb-32" id="pricing")
        div(class="container mx-auto p-4")
          span(class="text-xs text-gray-600 font-medium uppercase text-center block mb-1") Transparent, fair
          h3(class="font-bold text-center mx-auto text-4xl mb-28 sm:mb-16") Pricing

          div(class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start")
            div(class="flex-1 w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-md p-4 md:p-8 mb-8 md:mb-0 md:mr-8 bg-clip-padding bg-opacity-70" style="backdrop-filter: blur(20px);")
              div(class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-black mb-4 text-yellow-300") FREE
              h2(class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold") Creator Lite
              p(class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-4 md:mb-8") For the inspiration seekers.
              ul
                li(class="p-4 border-b")  One product page limit
                //- li(class="p-4 border-b") Collect products
                //- li(class="p-4 border-b") Boost products
                //- li(class="p-4 border-b") Boost posts
                //- li(class="p-4 border-b")
                //-   span Vote in surveys
                //-   span(class="uppercase ml-2 bg-yellow-50 rounded px-2 py-1.5 text-xs") Soon
                //- li(class="p-4 pb-0")
                //-   span Post comments
                //-   span(class="uppercase ml-2 bg-yellow-50 rounded px-2 py-1.5 text-xs") Soon
              div(class="mt-8")
                a(href="/login" class="btn btn-primary lg:text-xl text-center py-3 bg-yellow-100 hover:bg-yellow-200 transition") Join as Creator Lite
            div(class="flex-1 w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-md p-4 md:p-8 bg-clip-padding bg-opacity-70" style="backdrop-filter: blur(20px);")
              div(class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-black mb-4 text-yellow-300") 10$ / month
              h2(class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold") Creator
              p(class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8") For the doers.
              ul
                //- li(class="flex items-center p-4 border-b font-bold")
                //-   +icon("arrow-left")(class="mr-2")
                //-   span All from Creator Lite
                li(class="p-4 border-b text-xl") #[span(class="underline") Unlimited] product pages
                //- li(class="p-4 pb-0") All of Haptic's content creation tools
              div(class="mt-8")
                a(href="/login?creator=true" class="btn btn-primary lg:text-xl text-center py-3 transition") Join as Creator
  
  footer(class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center border-t border-gray-200 bg-white bg-opacity-70 bg-clip-padding py-24" style="backdrop-filter: blur(20px);")
    div()
      div(class="flex flex-col md:flex-row text-center md:text-left")
        div(class="mb-8 md:mb-0 md:mr-8")
          h4(class="text-xs text-gray-600 uppercase mb-4") Articles
          +footer-link("/how-to-build-in-public") How to build in public

        div
          h4(class="text-xs text-gray-600 uppercase mb-4") Legal
          +footer-link("/privacy-policy") Privacy Policy
          +footer-link("/terms-of-service") Terms of Service


    hr(class="w-10 border-gray-300 mx-auto my-8")

    p(class="text-xs") Built by #[a(href="https://twitter.com/Brslv" title="@Brslv" data-tippy-content="@Brslv on Twitter" class="text-yellow-400 underline hover:no-underline") @Brslv]
